title_narrative: Humanitarian mine action in West Bank NL MFA 2021-2022
sector_narrative: This project will clear three remaining minefields in Jenin and Tul Karem Districts, in the West Bank, towards the Palestinian goal of the West Bank being declared mine-impact-free. Clearance of these minefields will contribute to safety and improved livelihood opportunities for Palestinians.
description_narrative: This project will clear three remaining minefields in Jenin and Tul Karem Districts, in the West Bank, towards the Palestinian goal of the West Bank being declared mine-impact-free. Clearance of these minefields will contribute to safety and improved livelihood opportunities for Palestinians.

This project will clear three remaining minefields in Jenin and Tul Karem Districts, in the West Bank, towards the Palestinian goal of the West Bank being declared mine-impact-free. Clearance of these minefields will contribute to safety and improved livelihood opportunities for Palestinians.
The target groups for this project are landowners and communities living near minefields in West Bank.
